=head1 NAME

S246DSCS - Collects Discussions Information

=head1 DESCRIPTION

The following reports can be generated and are regrouped under C<Discussions>:

=cut

echo tput('bold'),'Processing Oracle Discussions module ...',tput('off')

# Initialization
var $ORACLE_HOME = getSetting('ORACLE_HOME','')
var $AGE         = getSetting('OCS_AGE',    15)
var $TAIL        = getSetting('OCS_TAIL1',  5000)

var $TOC = '%TOC%'
var $TOP = '[[#Top][Back to top]]'
pretoc '^1:Oracle Collaboration Suite'
pretoc '1+:Discussions'

# Load the common macros
run library()

=head2 Log Files

Gets the last lines of the log files.

=cut

debug ' Inside DSCS module, about to gather log files'
var $dir = catDir($ORACLE_HOME,'discussions','logs')
call sort_files(2,$TAIL,grepDir($dir,'\.log$','dir'))

=head2 not_found - Not found

Used as a warning when none of the Oracle Discussions files are found.

=cut

if !isTocCreated()
{debug ' Inside DSCS module, no file found'
 report not_found
 write 'No Oracle Discussions log files were found and all files were \
        optional. This does not mean there was necessarily a problem with RDA, \
        but it should be investigated.'
 toc '2:[[',getFile(),'][rda_report][Not found]]'
}

# Disable the group title in next index
toc '-:Oracle Collaboration Suite'

